{"id":"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator","title":"MaxLengthValidator","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\", \"name\": \"MaxLengthValidator\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L729-L784\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L729-L784\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"maxlengthvalidator\">MaxLengthValidator<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#maxlengthvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">該指令用於為帶有 <code><a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a></code> 屬性的控制項新增最大長度驗證器。該指令會提供 <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code>\n多重提供者列表。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A directive that adds max length validation to controls marked with the\n<code><a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a></code> attribute. The directive is provided with the <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> multi-provider list.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">表單驗證</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">Form Validation</a></p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n<h2 id=\"匯出自\">匯出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#匯出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">ReactiveFormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">FormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">選擇器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a>][<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a>][formControl]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a>][<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a name=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>屬性</th>\n        <th>說明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"maxlength\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a></span>: string | number | null</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">追蹤對此指令繫結的最小長度的更改。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Tracks changes to the minimum length bound to this directive.</p>\n</div>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n    <h3 id=\"adding-a-maximum-length-validator\" translation-result=\"on\">新增最大長度驗證器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#adding-a-maximum-length-validator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\">Adding a maximum length validator<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#adding-a-maximum-length-validator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">下面的例子示範瞭如何為一個帶有 ngModel 繫結的輸入框新增最大長度驗證器。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example shows how to add a maximum length validator to an input attached to an\nngModel binding.</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"html\">\n&lt;input name=\"firstName\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> <a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a>=\"25\"&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NgModelGroup\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/Validators\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/Input\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#adding-a-maximum-length-validator\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#description\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#instance-properties\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#maxlengthvalidator\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#see-also\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#selectors\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#匯出自\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#新增最大長度驗證器\n - api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - guide/form-validation\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L729-L784\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L729-L784\n-->"}